org.dapper.event

Class FlowEventBroadcaster

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dapper.event.FlowEventBroadcaster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<FlowEvent<?,?>>, Collection<FlowEvent<?,?>>, BlockingQueue<FlowEvent<?,?>>, Queue<FlowEvent<?,?>>

    public class FlowEventBroadcaster
extends Object
implements BlockingQueue<FlowEvent<?,?>>, Closeable
    A mechanism for broadcasting FlowEvents from the Dapper server to multiple subscribers in a thread-safe way.
